---
description: Authentication patterns
globs: src/**/*auth* , src/middleware.ts
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use @supabase/ssr for all auth operations in the app router.
- Server-side: use createServerClient from src/lib/supabase/server.ts
- Client-side: use createBrowserClient from src/lib/supabase/client.ts
- The middleware in src/middleware.ts handles session refresh. Do not modify it.
- To protect a page, check the session in the Server Component and redirect if not authenticated.
- Never expose SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY to the client.
